---
title: "02 | Wisdom"
author: "C.O."
date: "February 2026"
draft: false
---

The word "smart" is often used to describe wise people. Wisdom is more than being smart intellectually. Wisdom is having insight into situations and circumstances. The word of GOD declares in James that, if we lack wisdom, we should ask HIM for it. May we ask for wisdom to be our portion.

Meditate on these verses to gain wisdom:

-   Week 1
    -   Proverbs 3:13-18
-   Week 2
    -   Matthew 7:24
-   Week 3
    -   Isaiah 11:2
-   Week 4
    -   Psalms 104:24-25


